  "instructions": [
    "Heat the copper pot over medium heat and add the beurre monte.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the red curry paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the mixed vegetables, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the brown rice and water, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and stir in the chopped parsley.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
